			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Norwich O.</placeName> <date>Oct 19. 1852</date>.</p>
			<p><addressee>Rev Mr Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir&#44;</p>
          <p rend="indent(3)">I send you <sic>inclosed</sic><lb/> my own debt and that of my father to you.<lb/> I would be glad to know that it has not<lb/> been inconvenient to you that i have de&#61;<lb/>layed so long. I have recommended<lb/> the Occident to three or four here&#44; but they<lb/> have not allowed me to send their<lb/> names as your subscribers. They say they<lb/> will consider about it and finally they<lb/> reply that they take so many periodicals<lb/> that they have no room for an additional<lb/> one so expensive.</p>
          <p rend="indent(9)">Believe me</p>
          <p rend="indent(10)">Yours most respectfully</p>
          <p rend="indent(11)"><persName role="author">M. R. Miller</persName>.</p>
          
        </body>
    </text>
